milestones.description: David Lloyd's 116 is the highest individual score in ODIs (for ENG), surpassing Dennis Amiss's 103
Majid Khan's 109 is the highest individual score in ODIs (for PAK), surpassing Sadiq Mohammad's 37
Majid Khan has broken the record for most runs in boundaries (70) in an innings in ODIs for PAK, going past Sadiq Mohammad's 28
David Lloyd's 116 is the highest individual score in ODIs, surpassing Fredericks's 105
Majid Khan's 109 is the highest individual score in ODIs, surpassing Fredericks's 105
Majid Khan has become the top scorer for PAK in ODIs with 117 runs, going past Sadiq Mohammad's 37
Majid Khan has broken the record for most runs in boundaries (70) in an innings in ODIs, going past Ken Wadsworth's 64
Intikhab Alam has conceded the most runs in an innings (58) in ODIs for PAK, going past Sarfraz Nawaz's record of 46
Chris Old has conceded the most runs in an innings (65) in ODIs for ENG, going past Tony Greig's record of 63
Asif Iqbal has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (2) for PAK, going past Asif Masood
Majid Khan and Sadiq Mohammad's 113-run partnership is the highest for the 1st wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 96 between Geoff Boycott and Dennis Amiss
Mike Denness and David Lloyd's 103-run partnership is the highest for the 3rd wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 74 between Ian Chappell and Greg Chappell
Majid Khan and Sadiq Mohammad's 113-run partnership is PAK's highest for any wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 43 between Sadiq Mohammad and Intikhab Alam
Mike Denness and David Lloyd's 103-run partnership is ENG's highest for the 3rd wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 38 between Dennis Amiss and Frank Hayes
Majid Khan and Sadiq Mohammad's 113-run partnership is PAK's highest for the 1st wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 43 between Intikhab Alam and Sadiq Mohammad
Majid Khan and Zaheer Abbas's 74-run partnership is PAK's highest for the 2nd wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 9 between Majid Khan and Sadiq Mohammad
Asif Iqbal and Zaheer Abbas's 12-run partnership is PAK's highest for the 3rd wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 8 between Mushtaq Mohammad and Sadiq Mohammad
Mushtaq Mohammad and Asif Iqbal's 47-run partnership is PAK's highest for the 4th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 11 between Mushtaq Mohammad and Asif Iqbal
